OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,FCampaigners have lost High Court
OL,7,Fchallenges over the expansion of
OL,8,FGatwick Airport.
OL,10,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,11,Fapproved the #2.2 billion scheme in
OL,12,FSeptember, which would have seen the
OL,13,Fairport move its emergency runway 12
OL,14,Fmetres north to accommodate around
OL,15,F100,000 more flights a year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
