FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,FCampaigner Peter Barclay and campaign
OL,7,Fgroup Communities Against Gatwick
OL,8,FNoise Emissions (Cagne) took legal
OL,9,Faction against the Department for
OL,10,FTransport (DfT) over the decision,
OL,11,Ftelling a January hearing that it was
OL,12,Funlawful as the Government did not
OL,13,Fproperly assess the climate impacts of
OL,14,Fthe expansion.
OL,16,FThe DfT and the airport's owner,
OL,17,FGatwick Airport Limited, defended the
OL,18,Fchallenge, with lawyers for the site
OL,19,Fclaiming it was "unarguable".
OL,26,@{D@QOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,FIn a ruling on Tuesday, Mr Justice
OL,7,FMould dismissed Mr Barclay and Cagne's
OL,8,Fbids.
OL,10,FHe said in the 100-page judgment that
OL,11,FMrs Alexander concluded that while the
OL,12,Fproposed development will have
OL,13,Fmoderately adverse and significant
OL,14,Feffects, it will not "materially
OL,15,Fimpact" the Government's ability to
OL,16,Fmeet net zero targets.
OL,26,@vD@VOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,FThe judge continued: "The Secretary of
OL,7,FState for Transport does not resile
OL,8,Ffrom her finding that the proposed
OL,9,Fdevelopment will not fully contribute
OL,10,Fto the UK's trajectory towards net
OL,11,Fzero.
OL,13,F"On the contrary, that significant
OL,14,Feffect leads her to place moderate
OL,15,Fadverse weight against the making of
OL,16,Fthe development consent order.
OL,18,F"She does not, however, treat that
OL,19,Ffinding as determinative of her
OL,20,Fjudgment."
OL,26,@nD@VOUuD@AOUzD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,FMr Justice Mould concluded that it was
OL,7,F"neither illogical nor contradictory"
OL,8,Ffor Mrs Alexander to not refuse the
OL,9,Fproposed development "on the basis
OL,10,Fthat it would have a material impact
OL,11,Fon the ability of Government to meet
OL,12,Fits carbon reduction targets".
OL,14,FThe judge also rejected an argument
OL,15,Fabout the need for the expansion at
OL,16,FGatwick, given the proximity to
OL,17,FHeathrow.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@eO]qD@VOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,FHe said the Department for Transport
OL,7,Fhad considered that Gatwick is
OL,8,Fprimarily a leisure airport, largely
OL,9,Fserved by low-cost carrier flights,
OL,10,Fwith passenger numbers expected to
OL,11,Fgrow.
OL,13,FMr Justice Mould said Mrs Alexander
OL,14,F"considered both the need for and the
OL,15,Fsocio-economic effects of the proposed
OL,16,Fdevelopment to be important and
OL,17,Frelevant considerations" in making her
OL,18,Fdecision, adding: "Her conclusions are
OL,19,Frational and supported by proper,
OL,20,Fadequate and intelligible reasons."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@XO]zD@SOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,FIn a statement after the ruling, Cagne
OL,7,Fsaid it would not accept the judgment
OL,8,F"as the final word".
OL,10,FThe group said: "Our legal team will
OL,11,Fnow consider an appeal, and we will
OL,12,Fcontinue to stand up for the
OL,13,Fcommunities who will be forced to live
OL,14,Fwith the consequences of this
OL,15,Fexpansion.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]rD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,F"Cagne are obviously disappointed by
OL,7,Ftoday's ruling. Communities across
OL,8,FSussex, Surrey and Kent helped fund
OL,9,Fthis legal action because they have
OL,10,Fgrave and legitimate concerns about
OL,11,Fthe proposed expansion: the lack of
OL,12,Fairport funding for essential
OL,13,Finfrastructure, the absence of proper
OL,14,Finvestment in sewerage treatment, the
OL,15,Fincreased noise burden on local
OL,16,Fresidents, worsening air quality, and
OL,17,Fthe significant rise in CO2 and other
OL,18,Fharmful emissions.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,F"Today's ruling provides no
OL,7,Freassurance for those concerns. It
OL,8,Fdoes not change the fact that local
OL,9,Fcommunities are being asked to carry
OL,10,Fthe consequences while the airport
OL,11,Ffails to provide the funding needed to
OL,12,Fprotect the people and places affected.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,F"It is fundamentally wrong that
OL,7,Ftaxpayers should be expected to meet
OL,8,Fthe costs of new runway operations
OL,9,Fwhile shareholders stand to profit
OL,10,Ffrom an additional 101,000 flights a
OL,11,Fyear and 80 million passengers. The
OL,12,Fpublic should not be left to pay for
OL,13,Fthe infrastructure, environmental
OL,14,Fdamage and disruption created by
OL,15,Fprivate gain.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782310727
OL,3,CCampaigners lose High Court challenges
OL,4,Cover Gatwick Airport expansion
OL,6,F"This Government must stop viewing
OL,7,Faviation expansion through rose-tinted
OL,8,Fglasses and relying on unsubstantiated
OL,9,Fclaims of economic benefit while
OL,10,Fignoring the vast local and global
OL,11,Fenvironmental costs.
OL,13,F"Communities deserve honesty,
OL,14,Faccountability and protection ` not
OL,15,Fanother decision that sidelines their
OL,16,Fhealth, homes and environment."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
